 pornographic actress, model, and podcaster}}\n{{pp-pc1}}\n{{Infobox adult biography\n| name = Bailey Jay\n| image = Bailey Jay at AVN Awards 2011 1 (crop).jpg\n| caption = Bailey Jay at the 2011 AVN Awards\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1988|11|5}}<ref name=\"iafd\"/>\n| birth_place = [[Richmond, Virginia]], [[United States]]<ref name=\"iafd\"/>\n| birth_name =\n| spouse = Matthew Terhune\n| death_date =\n| height = {{height|ft=5|in=5}}<ref>{{cite tweet |user=baileyjaytweets |number=731192816290963458 |date=May 13, 2016 |title=I try not to be vain but somebody tell Wikipedia I'm actually only 5'5 lol.}}</ref>{{r|iafd}}\n| weight = {{convert|132|lb|kg|abbr=on}}<ref name=\"About Me\"/>\n| alias = Harley Quinn,<ref name=\"iafd\"/>  Line Trap<ref name=\"autogenerated1\">{{cite web |url=http://news.avn.com/company-news/Ts-Newcomer-Sensation-Bailey-Jay-Launches-Official-Website-398705.html |title=AVN \u2013 TS Newcomer Sensation Bailey Jay Launches Official Website |publisher=News.avn.com |date=2010-06-01 |accessdate=2012-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120428015317/http://news.avn.com/company-news/Ts-Newcomer-Sensation-Bailey-Jay-Launches-Official-Website-398705.html |archive-date=2012-04-28 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n| website = {{URL|http://www.ts-baileyjay.com/}}\n}}\n\n'''Bailey Jay''' (born November 5, 1988) is an American [[pornographic actress]], [[Fetish model|adult model]], and [[podcaster]].<ref name=\"iafd\">{{cite web|title=Bailey Jay |publisher=IAFD.com |url=http://www.iafd.com/person.rme/perfid=BaileyJay/gender=m/Bailey-Jay.htm |accessdate=2011-02-08 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101023171749/http://www.iafd.com/person.rme/perfid%3Dbaileyjay/gender%3Dm/bailey-jay.htm |archivedate=2010-10-23 }}</ref>\n\n==Career==\nIn 2011 and 2012, Jay won the [[AVN Award]] for [[transgender]] performer of the year.<ref name=avn11win>{{cite web  | title =Bailey Jay is AVN Transsexual Performer of the Year | publisher = AVN.com| url =http://business.avn.com/company-news/Superstarlet-BAILEY-JAY-Wins-AVN-Transsexual-Performer-of-the-Year-423222.html | date = 2011-01-14| accessdate = 2011-02-08}}</ref><ref name=avn12win/> She also co-hosts the [[podcast]] ''The Bailey Jay Show'' (formerly ''Bailey Jay Radio'') with her husband, photographer Matthew Terhune, the podcast ''The Trans Witching Hour with Bailey Jay'' (formerly ''Gender Coaching with Bailey Jay'') that deals with spirituality, the horror-themed podcast ''Blood Lust with Bailey Jay'' and also co-hosts the [[transgender]] and [[transsexuality]] advice podcast ''Sugar and Spice'' (formerly ''Third Gender Radio'') with Jen Richards of [[We Happy Trans]].\n\n==Filmography and appearances==\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2014\n| American Dream\n| Mom 2\n| Cary Nokey video\n|}\n\n===Web===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''The [[Jim Norton (American comedian)|Jim Norton]] Show''\n| Co-Host/Announcer\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''NICE TIPS!''\n| Advice columnist\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''The Approval Matrix'' \n| Herself\n| Episode: \"America's Hall Monitors\"\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Inside Amy Schumer]]''\n| Herself\n| Episode: \"Last Fuckable Day\"\n|}\n\n===Podcasts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Date\n! Title\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2010\u2013present\n| ''The Bailey Jay Show'' (with Matt Terhune)\n| Weekly podcast <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.riotcast.com/baileyjay|title=The Bailey Jay Show|work=riotcast.com|accessdate=18 September 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Robert Kelly (comedian)|You Know What Dude]]''\n| Two appearances<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.robertkelly.libsyn.com/webpage/2011/11|title=Robert Kelly's 'You Know What Dude!'|work=libsyn.com|accessdate=18 September 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''The Hole''\n| Episode 176<ref>{{cite we